# Media Library Management System (C++)

A console-based program that manages a collection of media items (books, movies, TV episodes) using Object-Oriented Programming.

## Features
- Reads and parses CSV files (`books.csv`, `movies.csv`, `tvShows.csv`)
- Classes with inheritance and polymorphism (`Book`, `Movie`, `TvShow`, `Collection`)
- Basic search/list display of media items
- Modular C++ design with headers (`.h`) and sources (`.cpp`)

## Tech Stack
- C++ (OOP, file I/O)
- Visual Studio / MSVC
- CSV file handling


